snippet.title: Eden's Edge (1.21) - Original 1cc (39,121,290)
snippet.description: A much more competent run (1-miss!) thanks to just one extra day of relaxed practice. To give an estimate, in the last run I fully knew what I was doing 50% of the time, while here it's closer to 80%. Still, this run does have it derpy moments, like an enemy surviving at the end of stage 3 (7:48) that I was completely unprepared to deal with. Anyway, quite a good run overall that puts me really close to mastering the Original mode.
